%% NASee 时序图 — 完整版

%% ==================== 1. 视频扫描流程 ====================
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Main as main.go
    participant Cfg as Config
    participant DB as Database
    participant Scan as Scanner
    participant Worker as FFProbeWorker
    participant Repo as VideoRepo
    participant FS as Filesystem

    Main->>Cfg: Load()
    Cfg-->>Main: *Config{MediaDir, DataDir, ...}

    Main->>DB: New(dataDir/nasee.db)
    Main->>DB: Migrate()
    DB-->>Main: tables created (videos, likes)

    Main->>Scan: Start(ctx)
    activate Scan

    loop 扫描循环 (间隔 = ScanInterval)
        Scan->>FS: filepath.Walk(MediaDir)
        FS-->>Scan: 文件列表 (按扩展名过滤)

        loop 每个视频文件
            Scan->>Repo: check by FilePath + ModTime
            alt 文件不存在 或 ModTime 已变
                Scan->>Worker: Probe(filePath)
                activate Worker
                Worker->>Worker: semaphore.acquire (max 2)
                Worker->>FS: exec ffprobe -v quiet -print_format json filePath
                FS-->>Worker: JSON metadata {duration, width, height}
                Worker->>Worker: timeout check (30s)
                Worker-->>Scan: *VideoMeta
                deactivate Worker
                Scan->>Repo: Upsert(Video{FilePath, Title, Duration, ...})
            else 文件已存在且未变
                Note over Scan: 跳过 (增量扫描)
            end
        end

        Scan->>Repo: MarkStale(scannedAt)
        Note over Repo: 删除文件系统中已不存在的记录

        Scan->>Scan: sleep(ScanInterval)
    end

    deactivate Scan

%% ==================== 2. 客户端连接 + 获取列表 + 播放流程 ====================
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 用户
    participant App as NASee App
    participant CVM as ConnectionViewModel
    participant ECS as EncryptedConfigStore
    participant API as ApiService (Retrofit)
    participant Server as NASee Server
    participant PM as VideoPlayerManager
    participant EP as ExoPlayer

    Note over User,App: 首次打开 / 无已保存配置
    User->>App: 打开 App
    App->>CVM: loadSavedConfig()
    CVM->>ECS: loadConfig()
    ECS-->>CVM: null (首次使用)

    User->>App: 输入 NAS 地址 + 密码
    User->>App: 点击「测试连接」
    App->>CVM: testConnection(address, password)
    CVM->>API: GET /health (X-NASee-Key: password)
    API->>Server: HTTP GET /health
    Server-->>API: 200 OK {"status":"ok"}
    API-->>CVM: success
    CVM-->>App: 连接成功

    User->>App: 点击「保存」
    App->>CVM: saveConfig(config)
    CVM->>ECS: saveConfig(ServerConfig{address, password})
    Note over ECS: Android Keystore 加密存储

    Note over App: 导航到 PlayerScreen
    App->>API: GET /api/v1/videos?page=1&page_size=20&sort=mod_time&order=desc
    API->>Server: HTTP GET (X-NASee-Key)
    Server->>Server: VideoRepo.List(filter)
    Server-->>API: 200 {videos:[...], total:150}
    API-->>App: VideoListResponse

    Note over App: 渲染 VerticalPager
    App->>PM: getOrCreatePlayer(videos[0])
    PM->>EP: new ExoPlayer()
    PM->>EP: setMediaItem(baseUrl + streamUrl, headers{X-NASee-Key})
    PM->>EP: prepare()
    EP-->>PM: ready (buffering complete)
    PM->>EP: play()
    EP-->>User: 视频开始播放

    Note over App: 预加载相邻视频
    App->>PM: getOrCreatePlayer(videos[1])
    PM->>EP: new ExoPlayer() + setMediaItem + prepare()

    Note over User,App: 用户上滑切换视频
    User->>App: 上滑 (VerticalPager settle)
    App->>PM: 切换 currentPlayer → videos[1]
    PM->>EP: play() (已预加载, 秒开)
    EP-->>User: 立即播放 (< 500ms)

    Note over App: 释放远端 Player, 预加载下一个
    App->>PM: releasePlayer(videos[-1])
    App->>PM: getOrCreatePlayer(videos[2]) + prepare()

    Note over User,App: 滚动到底部加载更多
    App->>API: GET /api/v1/videos?page=2&...
    API->>Server: HTTP GET
    Server-->>API: 200 {videos:[...]}
    API-->>App: 追加到列表

%% ==================== 3. 点赞流程 ====================
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 用户
    participant UI as PlayerScreen UI
    participant PVM as PlayerViewModel
    participant API as ApiService (Retrofit)
    participant Server as NASee Server
    participant LH as LikeHandler
    participant LR as LikeRepo
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over User,UI: 方式1: 双击屏幕 (同时触发点赞)
    Note over User,UI: 方式2: 点击右侧心形按钮

    User->>UI: 双击屏幕 / 点击心形
    UI->>UI: 播放点赞动画 (爱心粒子 + 按钮缩放)
    UI->>PVM: toggleLike(video.id)

    PVM->>PVM: optimistic update (liked = !liked)
    Note over PVM: 先更新本地 UI 状态, 保证即时反馈

    PVM->>API: POST /api/v1/videos/{id}/like (X-NASee-Key)
    API->>Server: HTTP POST
    Server->>LH: ToggleLike(videoID)
    LH->>LR: ToggleLike(videoID)
    LR->>DB: INSERT OR DELETE FROM likes
    DB-->>LR: success
    LR-->>LH: liked = true (或 false)
    LH-->>Server: {video_id, liked}
    Server-->>API: 200 {code:0, data:{video_id, liked}}
    API-->>PVM: LikeResponse

    alt 服务器返回与预期一致
        PVM->>UI: 保持动画状态
    else 服务器返回不一致 (如已被取消)
        PVM->>UI: 回滚 UI 状态
        UI->>User: 显示 toast "操作失败"
    end
